    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 requirements for MRL 2 Class II devices. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate sufficient accuracy (mean NIH error 5.7%) to support identification of worst-case operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. The simulation credibility evidence package is accepted for regulatory submission in support of 510(k) predicate comparison.",
